🚀 AI-Powered Mail Reply Assistant

An intelligent email reply assistant powered by Google Gemini AI, built with React, Spring Boot, and a Chrome Extension.

📝 Overview

This project is an AI-driven email assistant that helps users generate smart, context-aware replies within Gmail. It seamlessly integrates:

✅ Google Gemini API for AI-powered email response generation.

✅ React.js for the frontend UI.

✅ Spring Boot for backend processing.

✅ Chrome Extension for direct Gmail integration.

🌟 Features

✨ AI-Powered Email Reply Generation – Generate context-aware email responses in seconds.

✨ Seamless Gmail Integration – Works as a Chrome Extension to enhance your Gmail experience.

✨ Real-Time AI Processing – Uses Spring Boot to process requests efficiently.

✨ Localhost Deployment – Runs smoothly on your local machine.

✨ Customizable Tone – Adjust the tone of replies (e.g., formal, casual, professional).

🛠 Tech Stack

Technology

Purpose

Frontend

React.js

Backend

